data.description: Wonderful, Well Maintained End Unit in Thorncreek Village Condominiums*Bright and Open Kitchen*Spacious Cabinets for Storage*Under Cabinet Lighting*Double Sink*All Appliances Included*Smooth Top Stove*Extended Bar Counter*Separate Dining Area*Tranquil Primary Suite*Large Windows*Let in Natural Light*Gas Fireplace Centrally Located*Double Closet Provides Plenty of Storage*Separate Sitting Area* Primary Bath*Deep Soaking Tub and Rain Head Shower*Second Bedroom can be Guest Room or Home Office*Laundry Room includes Washer & Dryer*New Furnace & HVAC in 2021*New Roof & Gutters in 2021*HOA Fees Include Maintenance Grounds, Outdoor Pool, Snow Removal, Exterior Maintenance, Trash, Recycling, Landscaping, and Water (Interior-Water & Irrigation)$245 Monthly*Charming Backyard* Backs to Thorncreek Golf Course*Fully Fenced Yard includes a Side Gate Entrance*Outdoor Patio Area is a Perfect Spot for a Barbecue* Fantastic Location!*Thornton Creek Golf Course*Denver Premier Shopping Outlets and Restaurants Nearby*Big Dry Creek has Paved Hiking and Biking Trails
